<p sourcefile="finance/fixed-assets/200-percent-reducing-balance-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="84">The 200% reducing balance method divides 200 percent by the service life years. That percentage will be multiplied by the net book value of the asset to determine the depreciation amount for the year.</p>
