<div class="NOTE" sourcefile="finance/fixed-assets/200-percent-reducing-balance-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="92">
<h5>Note</h5>
<p sourcefile="finance/fixed-assets/200-percent-reducing-balance-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="93">Typically, when the amount that is calculated by using the 200% reducing balance depreciation method becomes less than the amount that would be calculated by using the straight line method, there is a conversion to the straight line method for the remaining life.</p>
